  "name": "{{.ClusterName}}",
  "completeness": 0.35,
  "issues": [
    {
      "id": "issue-id",
      "identifier": "AWE-50",
      "title": "Issue Title",
      "completeness": 0.4,
      "gaps": ["DoD missing", "No dependency specified"]
    }
  ],
  "observations": ["Cross-cluster findings"]
}
```

Important: Write output directly to the file path above. Do not write to stdout.
